# append(_:)

**Instance Method**

Appends the specified data to the end of this data.

## Declaration

```swift
mutating func append(_ other: Data)
```

## Adding Bytes

- **append(_:)**: Append a buffer of bytes to the data.
- **append(_:count:)**: Appends the specified bytes from memory to the end of the data.
- **append(contentsOf:)**: Appends the bytes in the specified array to the end of the data.
